text.section:
"Attendant services and supports" means any of the following services for a consumer, which are certified as necessary by a health care professional:
Dressing;
Preparing food and assisting with eating;
Bathing and personal hygiene;
Assisting with routine bodily functions, including bowel and urinary care;
Moving into, out of, or turning in bed;
Laundering and other clothing care; and
Cleaning house and performing other services of daily care, including shopping and transportation, that the consumer and the Department request.
